  renderPathForWeight(weight, color, pathsByWeight);

const Diamond = forwardRef<SVGSVGElement, IconProps>((props, ref) => (
  <IconBase ref={ref} {...props} renderPath={renderPath} />
));

Diamond.displayName = "Diamond";

export default Diamond;
